Update/Edit a post or a custom post type posts with Gravity Forms.

== Description ==

This simple Gravity Forms Add-On allows to update/edit/change existing posts or custom post type posts.

How to use:

- In form settings open "Post Update"
- Press "Add New"
- (Required) Enter "Post ID" number (OR insert a merge tag that will contain the ID)
- Configure new Author ID
- Configure new Post Status
- Configure Post title and desctiption manually or insert merge tags
- Leave any of above empty to avoid changes
- Configure your custom fields
- Configure conditional logic
- Press "Save Settings"

Features:

* Update "Post Author"
* Update "Post Status"
* Update "Post Title"
* Update "Post Content"
* Update "Post Custom Fields"
* Merge tags support
* Conditional logic support

== Installation ==

1. Install the plugin either via the WordPress.org plugin directory, or by uploading the files to your server
2. Activate the plugin via the Plugins admin page.

